le=\"color: #89DDFF\">&gt;</span>\n<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">    </span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&lt;</span><span style=\"color: #F07178\">head</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&gt;</span>\n<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">        </span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&lt;</span><span style=\"color: #F07178\">meta</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #FFCB6B\">charset</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">=</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">\"</span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">utf-8</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">\"</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&gt;</span>\n<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">        </span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&lt;</span><span style=\"color: #F07178\">title</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&gt;&lt;/</span><span style=\"color: #F07178\">title</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&gt;</span>\n<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">    </span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&lt;/</span><span style=\"color: #F07178\">head</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&gt;</span>\n<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">    </span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&lt;</span><span style=\"color: #F07178\">body</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&gt;</span>\n<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">        </span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&lt;</span><span style=\"color: #F07178\">script</span><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #FFCB6B\">src</span><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">=</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">\"</span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">script1.js</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">\"</span><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #FFCB6B\">defer</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&gt;&lt;/</span><span style=\"color: #F07178\">script</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&gt;</span>\n<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">        </span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&lt;</span><span style=\"color: #F07178\">script</span><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #FFCB6B\">src</span><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">=</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">\"</span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">script2.js</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">\"</span><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #FFCB6B\">defer</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&gt;&lt;/</span><span style=\"color: #F07178\">script</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&gt;</span>\n\n<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">        </span><span style=\"color: #676E95\">&lt;!-- Below elements are visible Before the script loading --&gt;</span>\n<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">        </span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&lt;</span><span style=\"color: #F07178\">div</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #FFCB6B\">class</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">=</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">\"</span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">parent</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">\"</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&gt;</span>\n<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">            </span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&lt;</span><span style=\"color: #F07178\">span</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #FFCB6B\">class</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">=</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">\"</span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">child1</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">\"</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&gt;</span><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Child</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&lt;/</span><span style=\"color: #F07178\">span</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&gt;</span>\n<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">        </span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&lt;/</span><span style=\"color: #F07178\">div</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&gt;</span>\n\n<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">    </span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&lt;/</span><span style=\"color: #F07178\">body</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&gt;</span>\n<span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&lt;/</span><span style=\"color: #F07178\">html</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&gt;</span></code></pre>\n<blockquote>\n<p>If you have a large script first, and then a smaller one, then the latter one waits.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"using-async-attribute\"><a href=\"#using-async-attribute\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>Using <code>async</code> attribute</h2>\n<p>Setting <code>async</code> attribute to a script tag will be loaded asynchronously, means it is completely independent of DOM. The HTML parser doesn't pause the DOM parsing, the the execution happens whenever the script becomes ready\nIf the async script is loaded before parsing the HTML completely, the parsing is paused and the script is executed and again the HTML parsing is started</p>\n<p>If we have multiple <code>async</code> scripts, they may execute in any order, which one loads first will be executed first</p>\n<p><img class=\"g-image g-image--lazy g-image--loading\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3csvg fill='none' viewBox='0 0 2560 536' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' xmlns:xlink='http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink'%3e%3cdefs%3e%3cfilter id='__svg-blur-267c89aea0cd04059600e7fa7334823e'%3e%3cfeGaussianBlur in='SourceGraphic' stdDeviation='40'/%3e%3c/filter%3e%3c/defs%3e%3cimage x='0' y='0' filter='url(%23__svg-blur-267c89aea0cd04059600e7fa7334823e)' width='2560' height='536' xlink:href='data:image/png%3bbase64%2ciVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAEAAAAANCAYAAAAZr2hsAAAACXBIWXMAACE4AAAhOAFFljFgAAAEtElEQVRIx82W%2bU9UVxSA/Rv6W5OmMdXauOGu2KK2dWm1IoqyDIJALLE2pm3SalttU9tobVPTaMUCAqK1bAJCYYYBlMgMMwzMAgOzoQwjKIxVoGpSU3WWr/e9YTGaNkYj%2bpIvZ7ln7rn3zH3v3AmM4xMMBp9q/OM8E8Z78/5AgEs9vXR7LtFz%2bQoDg0MM/XWDfu9VmctX%2bujpvYzP5xuXIox7Ae7evYe6rh6luo4OuxNLm1VIB/UNWhoa9TRodWj1Bv65c2d8CjCSIOgPELjnJ%2bB7MnxiHl8g%2bN%2bIcTmfIHAf0ph/eK9Bn5hDFEqSj7WG4KPgE/n8oRMwHu/a8/qMnoDr9RfpOqzFk2XAfaSRrkMa2Zb5RYs7vZHuDD3uozoxppX17oymUemRZGYTJRoPmWYvx1r6yDEKTP1kG0P6caFntYz5pJhcoeeZ%2b%2bWxHIsXY2Ebvek63GK%2bkfxukV/K6Zb8AmmN0vq6xVo8IqeElLsn3UB7kYYcb